OL,3,CStrictly dancer Amy Dowden made MBE
OL,4,Cfor raising awareness of bowel illness
OL,6,FAmy Dowden's sunny personality,
OL,7,Flilting Welsh accent and sparkling
OL,8,Fdance moves won her legions of fans as
OL,9,Fa professional on Strictly Come
OL,10,FDancing, but it has been her health
OL,11,Fstruggles that have endeared her even
OL,12,Ffurther to the general public.
OL,14,FAs an advocate and ambassador for
OL,15,Fcharity Crohn's & Colitis UK, she has
OL,16,Fbeen made a Member of the Order of the
OL,17,FBritish Empire (MBE) in the King's
OL,18,FBirthday Honours for her services to
OL,19,Ffundraising and raising awareness of
OL,20,Finflammatory bowel disease.
