OL,3,CStrictly dancer Amy Dowden made MBE
OL,4,Cfor raising awareness of bowel illness
OL,6,FThe 33-year-old, from Caerphilly, has
OL,7,Falso had a high-profile battle with
OL,8,Fbreast cancer and has undergone a
OL,9,Fmastectomy and chemotherapy.
OL,11,FShe first found a lump in her breast
OL,12,Fthe day before going to the Maldives
OL,13,Fon her honeymoon with fellow
OL,14,Fprofessional dancer Ben Jones and was
OL,15,Fsubsequently diagnosed with stage
OL,16,Fthree breast cancer.
OL,18,FShe recently finished chemotherapy and
OL,19,Ftests show she has "no evidence of
OL,20,Fdisease".
