OL,3,CStrictly dancer Amy Dowden made MBE
OL,4,Cfor raising awareness of bowel illness
OL,6,FEarlier this week it was announced
OL,7,Fthat she will rejoin the cast of
OL,8,Fprofessional dancers on Strictly for
OL,9,Fthe 2024 series after missing out last
OL,10,Fyear while she had treatment and also
OL,11,Fsuffered a broken foot.
OL,13,FIn 2019, Dowden revealed she was
OL,14,Fsuffering from Crohn's disease, and
OL,15,Ffronted the BBC programme Strictly
OL,16,FAmy: Crohn's And Me, in which she
OL,17,Fspoke about her battle with the
OL,18,Fcondition and met other people with
OL,19,FCrohn's to hear about their
OL,20,Fexperiences.
