OL,3,CStrictly dancer Amy Dowden made MBE
OL,4,Cfor raising awareness of bowel illness
OL,6,FPeople with the disease commonly
OL,7,Fexperience phases of intense abdominal
OL,8,Fpain, severe vomiting, exhaustion and
OL,9,Fbloody diarrhoea, among other symptoms.
OL,11,FDowden has previously said she was
OL,12,Fdiagnosed with the condition when she
OL,13,Fwas a child, but did not reveal she
OL,14,Fhad it when she joined Strictly,
OL,15,Fbecause she "didn't want to be known
OL,16,Fas 'Amy with Crohn's'".
OL,18,FA former British national Latin dance
OL,19,Fchampion, Dowden joined Strictly in
OL,20,F2017, and in 2019 she was a finalist
OL,21,Fwith TV presenter Karim Zeroual.
